        <head xml:id="la30px-aaa919-Hd1e104">Proposition 18</head>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa919-d1e106"> Proposition 18 </p>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa919-d1e111"> With the monarchs of Castilla having universal lordship
          over the Indies, it is good that Indigenous kings and lords continue in power over their
          subject peoples, or anything they politically or royally rule. It is as with their
          previous emperors. It was good that these previous emperors had supreme and universal
          lordship over the various kings. </p>
